01:36:21.176 --> 01:36:24.811
¶ Never together
yet never apart ¶

01:36:24.813 --> 01:36:27.914
¶ It's my longing
that keeps me alive ¶

01:36:27.916 --> 01:36:33.052
¶ Like there's no tomorrow ¶

01:36:33.455 --> 01:36:35.421
¶ Tomorrow ¶

01:36:54.342 --> 01:36:58.077
¶ Where have you been ¶

01:36:58.079 --> 01:37:02.148
¶ All this while ¶

01:37:02.150 --> 01:37:06.019
¶ To find you near ¶

01:37:06.021 --> 01:37:10.356
¶ I close my eyes ¶

